{"id": 2035, "genre": 1000, "title": "那些主打“便携”的东西你最后为啥没有随身带？", "description": "把所有随身必备便携用品都带着，我可能得把通勤包换成麻袋先。（题图来自：giphy）", "record_count": 10471, "comment_count": 26, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171127173738XA9rbmHv5nf2oGwa.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-28T17:00:03Z", "questions": [{"id": 3343, "title": "那些主打“便携”的东西你最后为啥没有随身带？", "content": "那些主打“便携”的东西你最后为啥没有随身带？ ", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 251200, "content": "鸡肋，超薄充电宝容量小放久了就没电，关键时掉链子 ", "image": "img/option/option/20171128153117a6ZzcLP50Eu4limI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251201, "content": "功能落伍，便携相机、手电、化妆镜…一个手机就够了", "image": "img/option/option/20171128153137sNJR6ve95nTIFaVO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251202, "content": "性能低配，便携式音箱用不几次，音质还不如家用的好", "image": "img/option/option/20171128155244Bwrzv5K16O7fXQMk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251203, "content": "浓缩但不精华，便携口袋书，多半是工具书/名著精简版", "image": "img/option/option/201711281540417SWxOd8mFiRc9zD4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251204, "content": "噱头大过实用性，便携洗衣机去渍笔，最后还得漂洗晾晒", "image": "img/option/option/20171128155312cnlCamtiqkENdOj6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251205, "content": "名不副实，只是 size 稍微小点，就叫便携式办公设备（打印机、扫描仪）", "image": "img/option/option/20171128160113rJWhKQBfkUg7wP9b.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251206, "content": "没有配套设施也不方便…带便携餐具出门吃饭没地方洗", "image": "img/option/option/20171128160207PFVckyqu73Yf6WRn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251207, "content": "设计不科学，便携茶具烫手、压缩水杯不占地但易变形", "image": "img/option/option/20171128160221uJ4AYGy3eMk1dlnv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251208, "content": "懒人真的啥也不需要，出门钱包都懒得带，带啥便携化妆品榨汁机 ", "image": "img/option/option/20171128160258y8EdRtXiUZFrwPjk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251209, "content": "？？？便携式剃须刀，剃须刀本来还不够便携吗？", "image": "img/option/option/20171128154056RgBKX8iOhq6bWQcn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}